channel.title: Help me unblock port 43594 on firewall please
channel.description:
so i tired to get my server online by port forwarding and after im done i go to canyouseeme.org and it says Error: I could not see your service on (ip) on port (43594) Reason: Connection timed out so someone told me that my fire wall is blocking port 43594 (i even went to fire wall and did "new rule") so can anyone help me unblock port 43594? if you can [SIZE=5]i will give rep and thanks please help me[/SIZE]
add me on skype: ashraful.hassan2
